## Final Security Posture

**Overall Risk Level**: LOW (All critical issues resolved)

**Security Features Implemented**:
- Webhook URL validation with domain allowlist (HTTPS + domain check)
- AuthVerifier interface for identity verification (ready for API exposure)
- Input sanitization (reason field, error messages, display text)
- Webhook response validation (Slack 'ok', Discord message ID)
- HMAC-SHA256 audit trail signatures (tamper detection)
- Comprehensive trust model documentation (storage requirements)

